    "title_en": "Worldsheet for Generalized Veneziano Amplitudes",
    "abstract_en": "We present a worldsheet action that reproduces a class of dual resonance amplitudes discussed in the literature, which generalize the Veneziano amplitude for open strings. Our proposal builds on the chiral composite linear dilaton introduced recently. We further compute higher-point extensions and closed-string analogs, which exhibit partial crossing symmetry.",
